      <title>十天震撼乌克兰的世界在挑战基辅的回响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-03-08/trump-s-withdrawal-of-ukraine-support-reverberates-in-kyiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使对于一个曾经使用过敌对部队的城市，乌克兰的首都也从美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）突然撤回了“支持”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-03-08/trump-s-withdrawal-of-ukraine-support-reverberates-in-kyiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 07:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯说，在圣彼得堡附近的主要炼油厂被无人机击中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/russia-says-major-oil-refinery-near-st-petersburg-hit-by-drone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯说，圣彼得堡附近的一家主要的炼油厂遭到无人机袭击，而乌克兰报告说，在包括黑海的奥德萨（Odesa）在内的几个地区发动了袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/russia-says-major-oil-refinery-near-st-petersburg-hit-by-drone</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 06:46:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Starmer对英国的软性左右施加了强大的力量，特朗普改变了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/starmer-puts-hard-power-over-soft-left-in-uk-changed-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）的盟友认为，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统陷入欧洲的危机可能是英国首相的制造。他们还说接下来可能会很容易地打破他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/starmer-puts-hard-power-over-soft-left-in-uk-changed-by-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸Junta Boss说，最早将在12月举行民意调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/myanmar-junta-boss-says-polls-to-be-held-in-december-at-earliest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[军政府在明斯克举行的一次州级会议上说，缅甸长期宣布的大选将于明年12月或明年1月举行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/myanmar-junta-boss-says-polls-to-be-held-in-december-at-earliest</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 04:33:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜领导人游览海军造船厂，南方就绪演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/north-korea-leader-tours-navy-shipyard-as-us-south-ready-drills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据州媒体的报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩在海军造船厂之旅期间开发了能够发射导弹的潜艇的发展，这可能是向美国和韩国部队发出的警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/north-korea-leader-tours-navy-shipyard-as-us-south-ready-drills</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 03:02:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对加拿大油菜油，猪肉设定了报复性关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/china-imposes-retaliatory-tariffs-on-canada-rapeseed-oil-pork</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，随着贸易战争的升级，它将对加拿大的油菜油，猪肉和海鲜进口征收报复性关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/china-imposes-retaliatory-tariffs-on-canada-rapeseed-oil-pork</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 01:27:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对乌克兰保持压力，因为普京对停火开放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/russia-s-putin-is-said-to-be-ready-to-agree-to-ukraine-truce-with-conditions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对乌克兰（Ukraine）的压力保持了一项和平协议的压力，因为信号表明克里姆林宫愿意在某些条件下接受临时休战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/russia-s-putin-is-said-to-be-ready-to-agree-to-ukraine-truce-with-conditions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 01:21:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Newsom命令重做加利福尼亚地标反塑造规则的重做，并以成本为由</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/newsom-orders-redo-of-california-s-landmark-anti-plastic-rules-citing-cost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加利福尼亚州州长加文·纽瑟姆（Gavin Newsom）告诉州监管机构，请务必遵循扫描委员会，以大幅度减少一次性塑料，理由是对措施的成本感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/newsom-orders-redo-of-california-s-landmark-anti-plastic-rules-citing-cost</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 23:03:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法院顾问说，亚当斯案件应永久抛弃。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/adams-case-should-be-permanently-dismissed-court-adviser-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）迈出了一步，以摆脱刑事指控的威胁，法官监督其腐败案件被敦促被任命为建议他的律师永久驳回其腐败案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/adams-case-should-be-permanently-dismissed-court-adviser-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 22:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普限制了非营利工人的贷款宽恕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-plans-to-restrict-loan-forgiveness-for-non-profit-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统签署了一项行政命令，该命令限制了政府经营的学生贷款宽恕计划的资格，其目标是针对非营利组织与政府移民和其他政策发生冲突的个人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-plans-to-restrict-loan-forgiveness-for-non-profit-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 17:48:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
